title: Looking for a duo partner to boost with me
body:
Am a high diamond yi/twitch jng one trick. I am looking for someone to play with me on my journey to get to diamond on this acount. Hit me up in game or below on this post. I normally play late nights, 9pm+. Hope to see someone come join me on a smurf account. 

Thanks fellas

replies.body: Is it too late to join in? I am silver 1 player with adc main. And I am looking for experienced player like you to duo with me so I can get to gold by the end of this season.
